flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 49: Admin Console Frontend Architecture Flow

  AdminHome[Admin Console]
  KYC[KYC and compliance review]
  Anomaly[Anomaly triage dashboard]
  Finance[Escrow and disbursement operations]
  Moderation[Content moderation queue]
  Analytics[Platform analytics]

  Guard[Role-restricted action controls]
  Sensitive{Finance or compliance sensitive action?}
  DualApproval{Second approver confirmed?}
  Execute[Execute admin action]
  Audit[(Append admin audit log)]
  Deny[Unauthorized UI denial state]

  AdminHome --> KYC --> Guard --> Sensitive
  AdminHome --> Anomaly --> Guard --> Sensitive
  AdminHome --> Finance --> Guard --> Sensitive
  AdminHome --> Moderation --> Guard --> Sensitive
  AdminHome --> Analytics --> Guard --> Sensitive

  Guard -->|not allowed| Deny
  Sensitive -- No --> Execute --> Audit
  Sensitive -- Yes --> DualApproval
  DualApproval -- Yes --> Execute --> Audit
  DualApproval -- No --> Deny
